%N A015493 Inverse of 1484th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015493 Periodic with period length 1484. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015493 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015493/b015493.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015493 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1484.
%H A015493 <a href="/index/Rec#order_624">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 624.
%H A015493 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015493 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%t A015493 CoefficientList[Series[1/Cyclotomic[1484,x],{x,0,120}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Sep 29 2023 *)
%o A015493 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(1484)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
